Why Optiv?












At Optiv, we eat, sleep and breathe cyber security. It’s in our DNA. We believe that everything we do is to create confidence for a more connected world. 
Join Optiv, and join a group of brilliant and inspiring cyber security minds. You’ll make a difference every day in the lives of our clients, and you’ll have fun doing it. We surround ourselves with the brightest minds in cyber security, and we always have each other’s back. We are Optiv, and we can’t wait to meet you.












Join Our Team
Optiv is home to more than 1,500 employees, from white hat hackers and CISOs, to marketing experts, IT geeks and bright legal minds. Find your people.
Check Out Our Openings








 
 
 
