Optiv Security Inc. Key Developments

Optiv Security Inc. Presents at Black Hat Conference, Jul-26-2017 10:30 AM
Jul 21 17
Optiv Security Inc. Presents at Black Hat Conference, Jul-26-2017 10:30 AM. Venue: Las Vegas, Nevada, United States. Speakers: John Ventura, Practice Manager for Applied Research.


Optiv Presents at Cloud Identity Summit 2017, Jun-19-2017 through Jun-22-2017
Jun 18 17
Optiv Presents at Cloud Identity Summit 2017, Jun-19-2017 through Jun-22-2017. Venue: Chicago, United States. Presentation Date & Speakers: Jun-19-2017, Aubrey Turner, Client Advisor - Identity Access Management. Jun-20-2017, Brian Vinacco, IAM Service Delivery Manager – Advanced Solution and Integration, Dan Olivares, Director, Cloud Security Programs, Dawn-Marie Hutchison, Executive Director, Office of the CISO, Ian Cumming, IAM Client Solution Advisor, Janel Shalk, Senior Director, IAM Advisory Solutions. Jun-21-2017, Bryan Wiese, VP & GM, Identity & Access Management, Richard Bird, ED, Executive Advisory; Office of the CISO. Jun-22-2017, Richard Bird, ED, Executive Advisory; Office of the CISO.


Optiv Security Appoints David Castignola as Executive Vice President, Worldwide Sales and Member of the Executive Leadership Team
Apr 11 17
Optiv Security announced the appointment of security sales executive David Castignola as the company’s first executive vice president of worldwide sales and a member of the executive leadership team. Castignola brings nearly 30 years of sales, marketing and operational experience to these roles, and will lead the sales organization as the company plans and executes on its previously announced global expansion.


